event Completed(uint256 indexed id, address winner)
event Created(uint256 indexed id, address indexed creator)
event NewBidder(uint256 indexed id, address bidder)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)

function auctions(uint256) view returns (address creator, address bidder, tuple(uint8 itemType, address addr, uint256[] amounts, uint256[] ids) item, uint256 minPrice, uint256 currentPrice, uint256 expiration, uint256 deadline, uint256 commission, uint8 status)
function create(tuple(uint8 itemType, address addr, uint256[] amounts, uint256[] ids) _item, uint256 _minPrice, uint256 _expiration) returns (uint256 id)
function onERC1155BatchReceived(address, address, uint256[], uint256[], bytes) returns (bytes4)
function onERC1155Received(address, address, uint256, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
